description.en:
Cats Claw Token ($CLAW) is the cat ecosystem token of meme culture. Cats Claw plans to counter the projects created via dog/inu ecosystem. 

Not only is our project solely a meme token, in the future we are adding functionality and utility by incorporating NFT/P2E/Metaverse. Our mission is the launch of the ClawSino, in which all individuals can participate with fun games such as Blackjack / Texas Hold Em' / etc. 

Cats Claw plans to incorporate all three aspects of NFTs / P2E / Metaverse into a fun community ClawSino that will mimic Las Vegas life.
